      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Deseed your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p><p>Chop your <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-6-1682418549009-x200.jpg",
